additionalProperty.name: Ingredients
additionalProperty.value: 5-15% Non-ionic surfactants, Oxygen-based bleaching agents, Polycarboxylates; <5% Phosphonates, Enzymes, Perfumes, Citronellol, Limonene, Linalool.

additionalProperty.name: Warning
additionalProperty.value: Danger CAUTION Causes serious eye damage. Keep out of reach of children. KEEP OUT OF REACH OF CHILDREN READ SAFETY DIRECTIONS BEFORE USE Contains no more than 20% w/w SODIUM PERCARBONATE Wear eye protection. NOT TO BE USED AS A FOOD CONTAINER. Do not dispose of unused tablets in the household waste bin but only via local council household chemicals collection process. Contains Sodium Carbonate Peroxide, Trideceth-n, Disodium Disilicate. FIRST AID For advice, contact a Poisons Information Centre (e.g. phone Australia 13 11 26; New Zealand 0800 764 766) or a doctor (at once).
